Thus the minerals found in the Dead Sea salts such as magnesium, calcium, iodine, zinc, bromide, potassium and sulfur are higher. There has been an increase in the use of Dead Sea Salts in beauty and health products to keep the skin healthy and well nourished. Dead Sea salt is most effective in cleaning the skin by natural exfoliation. It gets rid of toxins and helps in blood circulation. It relaxes the body by relieving body aches and pains.
